oid devices</li>\n<li>Fixed: Web-App Mode features displaying outside of Web-App Mode</li>\n<li>Fixed: Better audio, video handling in Web-App Mode</li>\n<li>Fixed: An issue which could cause Classic to show on tablet browsers w/o Tablet support enabled</li>\n<li>Changed: Social links in the footer now open in a new window</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a href=\"http://www.bravenewcode.com/2013/07/wptouch-pro-3-0-6-update-released/\">WPtouch Pro 3.0.6 Update Released</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.bravenewcode.com\">BraveNewCode Inc.</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"http://www.bravenewcode.com/2013/07/wptouch-pro-3-0-6-update-released/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"WPtouch Pro 3.0.5 Now Available!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"http://www.bravenewcode.com/2013/07/wptouch-pro-3-0-5-now-available/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"http://www.bravenewcode.com/2013/07/wptouch-pro-3-0-5-now-available/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_bas